</style><h2 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">活动概览</h2><h3 id="outline__1_1" class="wp-block-heading">门票发售纪念发行</h3><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[#FIRSTSTAGE]首次线下活动！门票发行纪念发放【6月29日举办🎉】" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/42i-9XKN-Tw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>日期和时间</td><td>2024 年 6 月 29 日星期六<br>开门时间：17:00 / 演出开始：18:00 / 预计结束时间：21:00</td></tr><tr><td>当地场地</td><td><a href="https://www.humax-cinema.co.jp/ikebukuro/news/80281/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="HUMAX 池袋电影院">HUMAX 池袋电影院</a></td></tr><tr><td>线上场地</td><td><a href="https://www.zan-live.com/live/detail/10420" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Z安">Z一N</a></td></tr><tr><td>查看票价</td><td>4,950日元（含税）</td></tr></tbody></table><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> *根据当天情况，时间可能会有所变化。</figcaption></figure><p></p><h3 id="outline__1_2" class="wp-block-heading">官方商品概览</h3><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczNy3QOtbuvuylgJkXua1ujah5DY1UzEZPLsSV8mS__JN810Ac1mcGjrIx7QSBWiS618QC0M6uFGzvVShd6_JxGRvP3WTKDy1dIw_Lqm911ILpLAfkWTSBKI50NJt0SRrXEpEyT-5-mfi0Pc3GSXVlgn=w1097-h617-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿©第一阶段制作</figcaption></figure><p>欲了解更多信息，请访问<a href="https://ichi-pro.booth.pm/items/5676344" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="第一阶段制作官方展位">FIRST STAGE PRODUCTION官方展位</a>。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-